snippet.textDisplay:
Hey Jimmy. This is so nice, thankyou. I would like to request, just in case it's possible, to see if you can do a show with BTS as a long distance guest. One thing the at home show needs is a laugh track for your funny jokes. You could interview BTS and ask if they can make a laugh track for your home show. It would be funny to see them trying to make each other laugh to get a good track. Jin especially has the most infectious windshield wiper laugh. You could challenge them to each bring a joke, impersonation of each other to see who can get the biggest laugh for the with track. I know ARMY would tune in every show just to hear your laugh track. lol.
